    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Sleeping With A Letter</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>It's to easy to forgive </l>
          <l>That is why you have to leave </l>
          <l>Look at me I'm sleeping with a letter </l>
          <l>Instead of you </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Though the world is full with hate </l>
          <l>Our island was filled with faith </l>
          <l>Look at me I'm sleeping with a letter </l>
          <l>Instead of you </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>I'm so hurt 'cause I love you so </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>How can I be sure at all? </l>
          <l>When you say that we won't fall </l>
          <l>Look at me I'm sleeping with a letter </l>
          <l>Instead of you </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Go to sleep my little one </l>
          <l>Dream a dream of golden sun </l>
          <l>Look at me I'm sleeping with a letter </l>
          <l>Instead of you </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>I'm so hurt 'cause I love you so</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
